%N A039101 Numbers whose base-9 representation has the same number of 3's and 8's.
%H A039101 Chris R. Rehmann, <a href="/A039101/b039101.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000</a>
%t A039101 Select[Range[0, 25426], DigitCount[#, 9, 3]==DigitCount[#, 9, 8]&] (* _Chris R. Rehmann_, Mar 19 2026 *)
%o A039101 (MATLAB) x = 0:25426; d = dec2base(x,9)-'0'; a = x(sum(d==3,2)==sum(d==8,2)); disp(regexprep(num2str(a), ' +', ', ')) % _Chris R. Rehmann_, Mar 19 2026
